  "title": "How we can end sexual harassment at work | Gretchen Carlson",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13700.0,
      "end_time": 16728.0,
      "text": "\"All I wanted was a much-deserved promotion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16752.0,
      "end_time": 18561.0,
      "text": "and he told me to &#39;Get up on the desk"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18585.0,
      "end_time": 20116.0,
      "text": "and spread &#39;em.&#39;\""
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21904.0,
      "end_time": 24651.0,
      "text": "\"All the men in my office wrote down on a piece of paper"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24675.0,
      "end_time": 27140.0,
      "text": "the sexual favors that I could do for them."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27583.0,
      "end_time": 30185.0,
      "text": "All I had asked for was an office with a window.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32189.0,
      "end_time": 35768.0,
      "text": "\"I asked for his advice about how I could get a bill out of committee;"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 36500.0,
      "end_time": 39267.0,
      "text": "he asked me if I brought my kneepads.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 41753.0,
      "end_time": 43991.0,
      "text": "Those are just a few of the horrific stories"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 44150.0,
      "end_time": 46523.0,
      "text": "that I heard from women over the last year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 46547.0,
      "end_time": 49726.0,
      "text": "as I&#39;ve been investigating workplace sexual harassment."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 50236.0,
      "end_time": 52385.0,
      "text": "And what I found out"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 52409.0,
      "end_time": 55225.0,
      "text": "is that it&#39;s an epidemic across the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 56307.0,
      "end_time": 59622.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a horrifying reality for millions of women,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 59646.0,
      "end_time": 61760.0,
      "text": "when all they want to do every day"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 61784.0,
      "end_time": 63204.0,
      "text": "is go to work."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 64998.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67247.0,
      "text": "Sexual harassment doesn&#39;t discriminate."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 67886.0,
      "end_time": 69268.0,
      "text": "You can wear a skirt,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 69799.0,
      "end_time": 71371.0,
      "text": "hospital scrubs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 71395.0,
      "end_time": 72683.0,
      "text": "army fatigues."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 73456.0,
      "end_time": 74976.0,
      "text": "You can be young or old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 75000.0,
      "end_time": 76215.0,
      "text": "married or single,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 76239.0,
      "end_time": 77429.0,
      "text": "black or white."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 77453.0,
      "end_time": 80693.0,
      "text": "You can be a Republican, a Democrat or an Independent."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 82577.0,
      "end_time": 85483.0,
      "text": "I heard from so many women:"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 86470.0,
      "end_time": 87402.0,
      "text": "police officers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 87427.0,
      "end_time": 88934.0,
      "text": "members of our military,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 88958.0,
      "end_time": 90414.0,
      "text": "financial assistants,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 90439.0,
      "end_time": 93651.0,
      "text": "actors, engineers, lawyers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 93676.0,
      "end_time": 96737.0,
      "text": "bankers, accountants, teachers ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 97485.0,
      "end_time": 98886.0,
      "text": "journalists."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 101521.0,
      "end_time": 103722.0,
      "text": "Sexual harassment, it turns out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 103746.0,
      "end_time": 105633.0,
      "text": "is not about sex."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 106609.0,
      "end_time": 108945.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s about power,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 108969.0,
      "end_time": 111539.0,
      "text": "and about what somebody does to you"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 111564.0,
      "end_time": 114104.0,
      "text": "to try and take away your power."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 114862.0,
      "end_time": 116470.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m here today"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 117285.0,
      "end_time": 122209.0,
      "text": "to encourage you to know that you can take that power back."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 123210.0,
      "end_time": 126273.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 127675.0,
      "end_time": 130234.0,
      "text": "On July 6, 2016,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 131300.0,
      "end_time": 133329.0,
      "text": "I jumped off a cliff all by myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 134685.0,
      "end_time": 136945.0,
      "text": "It was the scariest moment of my life;"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 136969.0,
      "end_time": 138995.0,
      "text": "an excruciating choice to make."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 141150.0,
      "end_time": 143873.0,
      "text": "I fell into an abyss all alone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 144688.0,
      "end_time": 146749.0,
      "text": "not knowing what would be below."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 148373.0,
      "end_time": 151798.0,
      "text": "But then, something miraculous started to happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 151822.0,
      "end_time": 154220.0,
      "text": "Thousands of women started reaching out to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 154460.0,
      "end_time": 157427.0,
      "text": "to share their own stories of pain and agony and shame."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 158132.0,
      "end_time": 160387.0,
      "text": "They told me that I became their voice --"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 160411.0,
      "end_time": 161942.0,
      "text": "they were voiceless."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 164293.0,
      "end_time": 167583.0,
      "text": "And suddenly, I realized that even in the 21st century,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 167607.0,
      "end_time": 170102.0,
      "text": "every woman still has a story."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 172796.0,
      "end_time": 174376.0,
      "text": "Like Joyce,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 175125.0,
      "end_time": 176647.0,
      "text": "a flight attendant supervisor"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 176671.0,
      "end_time": 178578.0,
      "text": "whose boss, in meetings every day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 178602.0,
      "end_time": 181739.0,
      "text": "would tell her about the porn that he&#39;d watched the night before"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 181763.0,
      "end_time": 183640.0,
      "text": "while drawing penises on his notepad."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 183664.0,
      "end_time": 184839.0,
      "text": "She went to complain."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 184864.0,
      "end_time": 186689.0,
      "text": "She was called \"crazy\" and fired."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 187219.0,
      "end_time": 189635.0,
      "text": "Like Joanne, Wall Street banker."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 189659.0,
      "end_time": 193233.0,
      "text": "Her male colleagues would call her that vile c-word every day."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 193258.0,
      "end_time": 194419.0,
      "text": "She complained --"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 194443.0,
      "end_time": 195784.0,
      "text": "labeled a troublemaker,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 195808.0,
      "end_time": 198539.0,
      "text": "never to do another Wall Street deal again."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 199438.0,
      "end_time": 202480.0,
      "text": "Like Elizabeth, an army officer."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 202831.0,
      "end_time": 206310.0,
      "text": "Her male subordinates would wave one-dollar bills in her face,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 206335.0,
      "end_time": 208630.0,
      "text": "and say, \"Dance for me!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 208456.0,
      "end_time": 210415.0,
      "text": "And when she went to complain to a major,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 210439.0,
      "end_time": 212983.0,
      "text": "he said, \"What? Only one dollar?"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 213700.0,
      "end_time": 215139.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re worth at least five or ten!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 218392.0,
      "end_time": 219965.0,
      "text": "After reading,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 219989.0,
      "end_time": 221576.0,
      "text": "replying to all"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 222277.0,
      "end_time": 226778.0,
      "text": "and crying over all of these emails,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 226802.0,
      "end_time": 230732.0,
      "text": "I realized I had so much work to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 232385.0,
      "end_time": 234530.0,
      "text": "Here are the startling facts:"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 234770.0,
      "end_time": 236129.0,
      "text": "one in three women -- that we know of --"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 236926.0,
      "end_time": 239700.0,
      "text": "have been sexually harassed in the workplace."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 240636.0,
      "end_time": 245789.0,
      "text": "Seventy-one percent of those incidences never get reported."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 246874.0,
      "end_time": 248240.0,
      "text": "Why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 248738.0,
      "end_time": 250435.0,
      "text": "Because when women come forward,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 250459.0,
      "end_time": 252590.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re still called liars and troublemakers"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 252614.0,
      "end_time": 254570.0,
      "text": "and demeaned and trashed"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 254594.0,
      "end_time": 256370.0,
      "text": "and demoted and blacklisted"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 256394.0,
      "end_time": 257765.0,
      "text": "and fired."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 257790.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262372.0,
      "text": "Reporting sexual harassment can be, in many cases, career-ending."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 263136.0,
      "end_time": 265289.0,
      "text": "Of all the women that reached out to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 266100.0,
      "end_time": 270873.0,
      "text": "almost none are still today working in their chosen profession,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 270898.0,
      "end_time": 272890.0,
      "text": "and that is outrageous."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 276360.0,
      "end_time": 279152.0,
      "text": "I, too, was silent in the beginning."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 280256.0,
      "end_time": 284366.0,
      "text": "It happened to me at the end of my year as Miss America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 284391.0,
      "end_time": 287530.0,
      "text": "when I was meeting with a very high-ranking TV executive"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 287770.0,
      "end_time": 288241.0,
      "text": "in New York City."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 288265.0,
      "end_time": 290493.0,
      "text": "I thought he was helping me throughout the day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 290517.0,
      "end_time": 291852.0,
      "text": "making a lot of phone calls."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 291876.0,
      "end_time": 293370.0,
      "text": "We went to dinner,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 293620.0,
      "end_time": 295985.0,
      "text": "and in the back seat of a car, he suddenly lunged on top of me"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 296900.0,
      "end_time": 297782.0,
      "text": "and stuck his tongue down my throat."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 299928.0,
      "end_time": 304356.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t realize that to \"get into the business\" -- silly me --"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 305608.0,
      "end_time": 308111.0,
      "text": "he also intended to get into my pants."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 310685.0,
      "end_time": 311930.0,
      "text": "And just a week later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 311954.0,
      "end_time": 316532.0,
      "text": "when I was in Los Angeles meeting with a high-ranking publicist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 316556.0,
      "end_time": 318750.0,
      "text": "it happened again."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 318990.0,
      "end_time": 319414.0,
      "text": "Again, in a car."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 319439.0,
      "end_time": 322410.0,
      "text": "And he took my neck in his hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 322434.0,
      "end_time": 325496.0,
      "text": "and he shoved my head so hard into his crotch,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 325520.0,
      "end_time": 327109.0,
      "text": "I couldn&#39;t breathe."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 333137.0,
      "end_time": 338622.0,
      "text": "These are the events that suck the life out of all of your self-confidence."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 341709.0,
      "end_time": 345866.0,
      "text": "These are the events that, until recently,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 345890.0,
      "end_time": 348270.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t even call assault."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 351455.0,
      "end_time": 355366.0,
      "text": "And this is why we have so much work to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 359431.0,
      "end_time": 361400.0,
      "text": "After my year as Miss America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 361424.0,
      "end_time": 363840.0,
      "text": "I continued to meet a lot of well-known people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 364899.0,
      "end_time": 366511.0,
      "text": "including Donald Trump."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 368500.0,
      "end_time": 370348.0,
      "text": "When this picture was taken in 1988,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 370372.0,
      "end_time": 372936.0,
      "text": "nobody could have ever predicted where we&#39;d be today."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 372960.0,
      "end_time": 374109.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 375239.0,
      "end_time": 378486.0,
      "text": "Me, fighting to end sexual harassment in the workplace;"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 379357.0,
      "end_time": 381793.0,
      "text": "he, president of the United States"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 381817.0,
      "end_time": 383890.0,
      "text": "in spite of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 386266.0,
      "end_time": 389297.0,
      "text": "And shortly thereafter, I got my first gig in television news"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 389321.0,
      "end_time": 390474.0,
      "text": "in Richmond, Virginia."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 390498.0,
      "end_time": 393279.0,
      "text": "Check out that confident smile with the bright pink jacket."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 393303.0,
      "end_time": 394530.0,
      "text": "Not so much the hair."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 394554.0,
      "end_time": 395703.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 396458.0,
      "end_time": 401169.0,
      "text": "I was working so hard to prove that blondes have a lot of brains."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 403270.0,
      "end_time": 405659.0,
      "text": "But ironically, one of the first stories I covered"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 405684.0,
      "end_time": 408225.0,
      "text": "was the Anita Hill hearings in Washington, DC."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 408663.0,
      "end_time": 410227.0,
      "text": "And shortly thereafter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 410251.0,
      "end_time": 413198.0,
      "text": "I, too, was sexually harassed in the workplace."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 414430.0,
      "end_time": 416488.0,
      "text": "I was covering a story in rural Virginia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 416512.0,
      "end_time": 418182.0,
      "text": "and when we got back into the car,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 418206.0,
      "end_time": 420850.0,
      "text": "my cameraman started saying to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 420109.0,
      "end_time": 422979.0,
      "text": "wondering how much I had enjoyed when he touched my breasts"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 423400.0,
      "end_time": 424577.0,
      "text": "when he put the microphone on me."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 424601.0,
      "end_time": 426388.0,
      "text": "And it went downhill from there."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 426947.0,
      "end_time": 429291.0,
      "text": "I was bracing myself against the passenger door --"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 429315.0,
      "end_time": 430848.0,
      "text": "this was before cellphones."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 430872.0,
      "end_time": 432118.0,
      "text": "I was petrified."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 432142.0,
      "end_time": 436204.0,
      "text": "I actually envisioned myself rolling outside of that door"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 436228.0,
      "end_time": 439457.0,
      "text": "as the car was going 50 miles per hour like I&#39;d seen in the movies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 439481.0,
      "end_time": 441588.0,
      "text": "and wondering how much it would hurt."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 445880.0,
      "end_time": 448862.0,
      "text": "When the story about Harvey Weinstein came to light --"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 448886.0,
      "end_time": 452305.0,
      "text": "one the most well-known movie moguls in all of Hollywood --"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 452329.0,
      "end_time": 454265.0,
      "text": "the allegations were horrific."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 454882.0,
      "end_time": 456849.0,
      "text": "But so many women came forward,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 456873.0,
      "end_time": 460497.0,
      "text": "and it made me realize what I had done meant something."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 461381.0,
      "end_time": 466506.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 468245.0,
      "end_time": 470274.0,
      "text": "He had such a lame excuse."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 470813.0,
      "end_time": 473193.0,
      "text": "He said he was a product of the &#39;60s and &#39;70s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 473218.0,
      "end_time": 474974.0,
      "text": "and that that was the culture then."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 474998.0,
      "end_time": 476877.0,
      "text": "Yeah, that was the culture then,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 476901.0,
      "end_time": 479798.0,
      "text": "and unfortunately, it still is."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 479822.0,
      "end_time": 480972.0,
      "text": "Why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 481779.0,
      "end_time": 483150.0,
      "text": "Because of all the myths"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 483174.0,
      "end_time": 485469.0,
      "text": "that are still associated with sexual harassment."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 487400.0,
      "end_time": 490239.0,
      "text": "\"Women should just take another job and find another career.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 490263.0,
      "end_time": 491417.0,
      "text": "Yeah, right."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 491441.0,
      "end_time": 493607.0,
      "text": "Tell that to the single mom working two jobs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 493632.0,
      "end_time": 495510.0,
      "text": "trying to make ends meet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 495750.0,
      "end_time": 496925.0,
      "text": "who&#39;s also being sexually harassed."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 498820.0,
      "end_time": 499627.0,
      "text": "\"Women --"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 499651.0,
      "end_time": 501422.0,
      "text": "they bring it on themselves.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 502500.0,
      "end_time": 503570.0,
      "text": "By the clothes that we wear"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 503595.0,
      "end_time": 505238.0,
      "text": "and the makeup that we put on."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 505876.0,
      "end_time": 509431.0,
      "text": "Yeah, I guess those hoodies that Uber engineers wear in Silicon Valley"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 509455.0,
      "end_time": 511217.0,
      "text": "are just so provocative."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 512639.0,
      "end_time": 513938.0,
      "text": "\"Women make it up.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 514619.0,
      "end_time": 517549.0,
      "text": "Yeah, because it&#39;s so fun and rewarding"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 517573.0,
      "end_time": 520158.0,
      "text": "to be demeaned and taken down."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 520182.0,
      "end_time": 521422.0,
      "text": "I would know."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 523323.0,
      "end_time": 527920.0,
      "text": "\"Women bring these claims because they want to be famous and rich.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 528456.0,
      "end_time": 530267.0,
      "text": "Our own president said that."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 532465.0,
      "end_time": 534286.0,
      "text": "I bet Taylor Swift,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 534310.0,
      "end_time": 538350.0,
      "text": "one of the most well-known and richest singers in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 538660.0,
      "end_time": 540328.0,
      "text": "didn&#39;t need more money or fame"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 540352.0,
      "end_time": 542557.0,
      "text": "when she came forward with her groping case"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 542581.0,
      "end_time": 543967.0,
      "text": "for one dollar."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 544688.0,
      "end_time": 546771.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m so glad she did."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 549180.0,
      "end_time": 550726.0,
      "text": "Breaking news:"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 550750.0,
      "end_time": 555310.0,
      "text": "the untold story about women and sexual harassment in the workplace:"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 556667.0,
      "end_time": 559498.0,
      "text": "women just want a safe, welcoming"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 559522.0,
      "end_time": 562320.0,
      "text": "and harass-free environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 562560.0,
      "end_time": 563257.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s it."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 564180.0,
      "end_time": 568967.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 570405.0,
      "end_time": 573476.0,
      "text": "So how do we go about getting our power back?"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 573500.0,
      "end_time": 575220.0,
      "text": "I have three solutions."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 575667.0,
      "end_time": 576817.0,
      "text": "Number one:"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 577219.0,
      "end_time": 581460.0,
      "text": "we need to turn bystanders and enablers into allies."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 581880.0,
      "end_time": 584918.0,
      "text": "Ninety-eight percent of United States corporations right now"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 584942.0,
      "end_time": 587650.0,
      "text": "have sexual harassment training policies."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 587890.0,
      "end_time": 590418.0,
      "text": "Seventy percent have prevention programs."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 590900.0,
      "end_time": 593790.0,
      "text": "But still, overwhelmingly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 593103.0,
      "end_time": 596348.0,
      "text": "bystanders and witnesses don&#39;t come forward."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 597225.0,
      "end_time": 598377.0,
      "text": "In 2016,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 598401.0,
      "end_time": 602334.0,
      "text": "the Harvard Business Review called it the \"bystander effect.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 603760.0,
      "end_time": 606686.0,
      "text": "And yet -- remember 9/11."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 607227.0,
      "end_time": 609780.0,
      "text": "Millions of times we&#39;ve heard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 609804.0,
      "end_time": 611208.0,
      "text": "\"If you see something,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 611232.0,
      "end_time": 612620.0,
      "text": "say something.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 613845.0,
      "end_time": 617691.0,
      "text": "Imagine how impactful that would be if we carried that through"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 617715.0,
      "end_time": 620754.0,
      "text": "to bystanders in the workplace regarding sexual harassment --"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 621933.0,
      "end_time": 625322.0,
      "text": "to recognize and interrupt these incidences;"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 626397.0,
      "end_time": 629699.0,
      "text": "to confront the perpetrators to their face;"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 630700.0,
      "end_time": 633511.0,
      "text": "to help and protect the victims."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 634279.0,
      "end_time": 636272.0,
      "text": "This is my shout-out to men:"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 636715.0,
      "end_time": 638935.0,
      "text": "we need you in this fight."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 639560.0,
      "end_time": 641185.0,
      "text": "And to women, too --"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 641209.0,
      "end_time": 644500.0,
      "text": "enablers to allies."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 644499.0,
      "end_time": 645855.0,
      "text": "Number two:"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 645879.0,
      "end_time": 647294.0,
      "text": "change the laws."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 649290.0,
      "end_time": 650467.0,
      "text": "How many of you out there know"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 650491.0,
      "end_time": 652910.0,
      "text": "whether or not you have a forced arbitration clause"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 652934.0,
      "end_time": 654832.0,
      "text": "in your employment contract?"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 656950.0,
      "end_time": 657245.0,
      "text": "Not a lot of hands."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 657269.0,
      "end_time": 658997.0,
      "text": "And if you don&#39;t know, you should,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 659210.0,
      "end_time": 660251.0,
      "text": "and here&#39;s why."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 661960.0,
      "end_time": 662352.0,
      "text": "TIME Magazine calls it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 662376.0,
      "end_time": 664150.0,
      "text": "right there on the screen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 664390.0,
      "end_time": 667394.0,
      "text": "\"The teeny tiny little print in contracts"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 667418.0,
      "end_time": 670801.0,
      "text": "that keeps sexual harassment claims unheard.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 671646.0,
      "end_time": 673150.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s what it is."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 673390.0,
      "end_time": 675833.0,
      "text": "Forced arbitration takes away your Seventh Amendment right"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 675857.0,
      "end_time": 677278.0,
      "text": "to an open jury process."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 677850.0,
      "end_time": 679000.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s secret."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 680105.0,
      "end_time": 682400.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t get the same witnesses or depositions."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 682424.0,
      "end_time": 685269.0,
      "text": "In many cases, the company picks the arbitrator for you."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 685855.0,
      "end_time": 688331.0,
      "text": "There are no appeals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 688355.0,
      "end_time": 691157.0,
      "text": "and only 20 percent of the time does the employee win."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 691927.0,
      "end_time": 693559.0,
      "text": "But again, it&#39;s secret,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 693583.0,
      "end_time": 696529.0,
      "text": "so nobody ever knows what happened to you."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 697732.0,
      "end_time": 699747.0,
      "text": "This is why I&#39;ve been working so diligently"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 699772.0,
      "end_time": 701404.0,
      "text": "on Capitol Hill in Washington, DC"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 701428.0,
      "end_time": 702580.0,
      "text": "to change the laws."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 702604.0,
      "end_time": 704420.0,
      "text": "And here&#39;s what I tell the Senators:"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 704444.0,
      "end_time": 706439.0,
      "text": "sexual harassment is apolitical."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 706464.0,
      "end_time": 708430.0,
      "text": "Before somebody harasses you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 708670.0,
      "end_time": 711801.0,
      "text": "they don&#39;t ask you if you&#39;re a Republican or Democrat first."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 711825.0,
      "end_time": 713119.0,
      "text": "They just do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 713143.0,
      "end_time": 715585.0,
      "text": "And this is why we should all care."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 716385.0,
      "end_time": 717535.0,
      "text": "Number three:"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 717940.0,
      "end_time": 719900.0,
      "text": "be fierce."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 719666.0,
      "end_time": 722269.0,
      "text": "It starts when we stand tall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 722293.0,
      "end_time": 724255.0,
      "text": "and we build that self-confidence."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 724279.0,
      "end_time": 726770.0,
      "text": "And we stand up and we speak up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 726101.0,
      "end_time": 728479.0,
      "text": "and we tell the world what happened to us."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 729932.0,
      "end_time": 731933.0,
      "text": "I know it&#39;s scary,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 731957.0,
      "end_time": 733737.0,
      "text": "but let&#39;s do it for our kids."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 734102.0,
      "end_time": 736956.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s stop this for the next generations."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 738777.0,
      "end_time": 741498.0,
      "text": "I know that I did it for my children."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 742835.0,
      "end_time": 745450.0,
      "text": "They were paramount in my decision-making"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 745690.0,
      "end_time": 747276.0,
      "text": "about whether or not I would come forward."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 747623.0,
      "end_time": 748917.0,
      "text": "My beautiful children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 748941.0,
      "end_time": 750704.0,
      "text": "my 12-year-old son, Christian,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 750728.0,
      "end_time": 752894.0,
      "text": "my 14-year-old daughter, Kaia."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 752918.0,
      "end_time": 754985.0,
      "text": "And boy, did I underestimate them."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 756164.0,
      "end_time": 757740.0,
      "text": "The first day of school last year"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 757764.0,
      "end_time": 760177.0,
      "text": "happened to be the day my resolution was announced,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 760201.0,
      "end_time": 762462.0,
      "text": "and I was so anxious about what they would face."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 762486.0,
      "end_time": 764699.0,
      "text": "My daughter came home from school and she said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 764723.0,
      "end_time": 768101.0,
      "text": "\"Mommy, so many people asked me what happened to you over the summer.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 768125.0,
      "end_time": 769746.0,
      "text": "Then she looked at me in the eyes"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 769770.0,
      "end_time": 771266.0,
      "text": "and she said, \"And mommy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 771291.0,
      "end_time": 772817.0,
      "text": "I was so proud"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 773794.0,
      "end_time": 776353.0,
      "text": "to say that you were my mom.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 778749.0,
      "end_time": 780900.0,
      "text": "And two weeks later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 780330.0,
      "end_time": 783987.0,
      "text": "when she finally found the courage to stand up to two kids"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 784110.0,
      "end_time": 786590.0,
      "text": "who had been making her life miserable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 786830.0,
      "end_time": 787698.0,
      "text": "she came home to me and she said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 787722.0,
      "end_time": 791170.0,
      "text": "\"Mommy, I found the courage to do it"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 791917.0,
      "end_time": 794489.0,
      "text": "because I saw you do it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 796510.0,
      "end_time": 803520.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 804487.0,
      "end_time": 808384.0,
      "text": "You see, giving the gift of courage is contagious."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 810394.0,
      "end_time": 813733.0,
      "text": "And I hope that my journey has inspired you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 813757.0,
      "end_time": 816520.0,
      "text": "because right now, it&#39;s the tipping point."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 816922.0,
      "end_time": 819234.0,
      "text": "We are watching history happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 819258.0,
      "end_time": 821662.0,
      "text": "More and more women are coming forward and saying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 821686.0,
      "end_time": 823460.0,
      "text": "\"Enough is enough.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 826360.0,
      "end_time": 829742.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 831412.0,
      "end_time": 834500.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s my one last plea to companies."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 834558.0,
      "end_time": 839300.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s hire back all those women whose careers were lost"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 839270.0,
      "end_time": 841360.0,
      "text": "because of some random jerk."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 842117.0,
      "end_time": 844171.0,
      "text": "Because here&#39;s what I know about women:"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 845116.0,
      "end_time": 849273.0,
      "text": "we will not longer be underestimated, intimidated or set back;"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 849881.0,
      "end_time": 853233.0,
      "text": "we will not be silenced by the ways of the establishment"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 853257.0,
      "end_time": 855185.0,
      "text": "or the relics of the past."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 855209.0,
      "end_time": 856358.0,
      "text": "No."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 856819.0,
      "end_time": 859442.0,
      "text": "We will stand up and speak up"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 860214.0,
      "end_time": 861942.0,
      "text": "and have our voices heard."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 862778.0,
      "end_time": 866517.0,
      "text": "We will be the women we were meant to be."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 867957.0,
      "end_time": 869914.0,
      "text": "And above all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 869938.0,
      "end_time": 873669.0,
      "text": "we will always be fierce."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 874196.0,
      "end_time": 875370.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 875701.0,
      "end_time": 880626.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}